title: Bookworm - Rabin Square
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Middle Eastern, Israeli, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe and bookstore where you can sit with a laptop or borrow a book from the cafe while you are there. Vegan items marked on the menu in every category, including breakfast, salads, sandwiches, mains, and desserts. Free Wi-Fi.
